{
  "stem": "3658.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the only thing that was different.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But can't remember them ever being anti-us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They might have been, but they didn't show it to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not actually yarmulke, but we had a hat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Listen, in that area of the world was so cold in any case, we had the hats.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the big hats, but just the same as they wear here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that part was all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very, very upset, and very worried.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mainly for the children, you can imagine, all of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How to feed, how to-- where we were going to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I'm sure my father, being a soldier-- you know, he was in the Czech army-- he would have known a lot more than he would have told us, because there was a whole group of the young men, you know, before, before they were taking us.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were soldiers in the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to, to-- so they would have known much more, and they would have been aware of what was happening.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would have read newspapers, too, what was happening, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we, the youngsters, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were told we were going to go to work, and we have to be-- And I remember my mother dressed me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how many shirts I had on, how many underwear, underpants I had on, and jackets and, you know, sweaters.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was looking like a barrel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I could hardly walk, but she said you'll need it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You'll need it because it'll get cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we can-- you know, you can take off layers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it has to be washed, and we don't know where we're going to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was every one of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
